            <p>Most residential driveways are completed within 1–4 days, depending on the size, surface type, and the extent of any groundworks required. Resin and tarmac driveways tend to be quicker, while block paving or concrete driveways with complex patterns or major ground preparation can take a little longer. We'll give you a realistic timeframe in your quote.</p>
